<C>__{drew}
<D>__{you got it.}
<A>__{before he can move, however, gao attacks, slamming him full power in the face. drew almost falls to the ground, then attacks him and the battle is joined. the fighting is fast and furious, and soon the others see what is happening, and gather around. one of the monks comes over and tries to break it up, but they continue fighting, wrestling, kicking and punching. the d.s. finally gets over to them, and without moving a muscle, barks}
